{"tid":924292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[說好的美國差佬大晒呢?]之前入錯屋開槍射死黑人既美國女警正式被起訴謀殺","createTime":"2018-12-02T03:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T04:42:19.000Z","uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2a05784f74ad93ee873238a09034e4507f7e6a","tid":924292,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.fox4news.com/media.fox4news.com/photo/2018/11/30/Former_Dallas_officer_Amber_Guyger_indic_0_6463853_ver1.0_640_360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.fox4news.com%2Fmedia.fox4news.com%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F11%2F30%2FFormer_Dallas_officer_Amber_Guyger_indic_0_6463853_ver1.0_640_360.jpg&h=b5a7340c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aYupdV8_OGg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaYupdV8_OGg&d=siact7mot2Oi48hSsu2n1dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b0349eab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aYupdV8_OGg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2018/11/30/us/dallas-police-officer-botham-jean/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F11%2F30%2Fus%2Fdallas-police-officer-botham-jean%2Findex.html&d=siact7mot2Oi48hSsu2n1dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bcd815de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F11%2F30%2Fus%2Fdallas-police-officer-botham-jean%2Findex.html&h=641b2e9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2018/11/30/us/dallas-police-officer-botham-jean/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n事源:<br />\n美國德州達拉斯（Dallas）一名26歲非裔男子謹恩（Botham Jean）6日遭到走錯家門的白人女警蓋格（Amber Guyger）意外槍殺，詳細案發原因還有待警方調查，不過謹恩的母親8日公開質疑兒子的種族問題或許是他遇害的因素之一。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，這起槍擊案發生在一棟高級的公寓大樓內，女警供稱她在晚間十點回到公寓後，因為以為是進到自己家，才會朝著屋內的陌生人謹恩開槍，驚覺自己走錯家門後才緊急打電話報警自首。<br />\n<br />\n謹恩的母親愛莉森向媒體表示，「兒子的死就像是一場噩夢」，得知開槍女警是白人後，她想知道如果謹恩也是白人，那自稱走錯家門的那名女警，反應會不會有何不同。<br />\n<br />\n代表達拉斯地區的州參議員韋斯特（Royce West）8日向媒體表示，此案是否與種族因素有關仍有待釐清，「我們要確認兩人是否有私交。在確定殺人案類型前，還有許多事情需要查明」。<br />\n<br />\n警官米歇爾（Warren Mitchell）提到，謹恩在送醫後不治，女警則沒有任何受傷，目前正被強制休假中。而關於金恩的房門當時是否有上鎖，且女警是如何進入謹恩房間等，都還有待調查釐清。目前已經採集這名女警的血液樣本，準備進行毒品和酒精測試。 警方打算就現有證據控告該女警過失殺人罪。<br />\n<br />\n謹恩去世後，愛莉森哀痛的表示，她想為兒子伸張正義並得到更好的解釋。她說：「我不想批判她，我們是基督徒。我們原諒。但我要看著她的眼睛，問她為什麼這樣對我的兒子。她取走了我的心、我的靈魂。」"},{"pid":"3a389cb8a8b0823317079dfdae9e26219e206e59","tid":924292,"uid":54876,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:57:05.000Z","msg":"一單半單算咩，警犬呢個職業已經係垃圾，讀唔成書拎支炮响度9 fing fing"},{"pid":"7b978645a2718e6448b794e259d17d0f4c9c0a62","tid":924292,"uid":35815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e16294b2cae22511012b61d8e99394e7fa371417","tid":924292,"uid":64191,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"非勤務殺人的確走唔甩啊"},{"pid":"53f045cfc851446ea4df98947a6440c7f0639440","tid":924292,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"美國差佬係咪勁大精神壓力"},{"pid":"c5e269c62f4ee4e0469875998fbbc4d533403ad2","tid":924292,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac354ddf854ac3e515f749580963a32f6c7a0991","tid":924292,"uid":118988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:02:54.000Z","msg":"起訴渣麻,都未判"},{"pid":"01a20453ed4441253f6446b5b4d373b1a2ebb9bb","tid":924292,"uid":1654,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac354ddf854ac3e515f749580963a32f6c7a0991","tid":924292,"uid":118988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:02:54.000Z","msg":"起訴渣麻,都未判"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"7 警拖兩年先告小罪"},{"pid":"cfc145d955f0f9a3e9f08440243752b1ba40368b","tid":924292,"uid":66686,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"01a20453ed4441253f6446b5b4d373b1a2ebb9bb","tid":92